    "While both GPT-3.5 and GPT-4 exhibit impressive multilingual understanding, a variety of empirical results have shown that large language models struggle to adequately understand and generate non-English language text (Bang et al., 2023; Jiao et al., 2023; Zhu et al., 2023).",
    "However, misinformation is a problem that is not restricted to highresource languages.",
